### 2. Polar Axis Electromagnetic Field Mapping

**Objective:**  
To measure and visualize the variation in Earth's electromagnetic field strength and orientation from the North Pole to the South Pole along the polar axis. This supports the Open Earth Polar Model's hypothesis that the polar axis is central to Earth's energetic behavior.

